{"tid":28373,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友同男仔friend一齊去旅行","createTime":"2016-12-08T01:52:20.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T15:56:22.000Z","uid":5812,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7e07834b8197b404193e3c09143a49ca0c34d2","tid":28373,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"上個禮拜，我女朋友同咗一個中學同學去台灣旅行，男仔嚟&hellip;佢話因為台灣有mutual fd，要兩個人一齊去搵佢，所以就兩個人一齊去&hellip;因為我請唔到假，就冇跟埋去（其實原本都好似冇預我咁）<br />\n<br />\n佢地係住hostel，有幾個人同房，冇瞓埋同一張床。但係我都有d唔開心，因為去旅行期間，我有每日夜晚打俾女朋友，但係通常女朋友都話未返到hostel或者同fd一齊，唔傾得耐。<br />\n<br />\n之後佢返到香港，我有一次忍唔住睇佢電話，啲旅行相都真係有個台灣fd喺度既，不過銀包入面啲信用卡單有啲係買男人野、高達模型..但又唔係買俾我嘅手信&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都盡量唔好諗咁多，唔去都去咗，但係都覺得好古怪...男女之間真係有純友誼？"},{"pid":"7209c9b409d946b1b4dd3dc22088cecd843124f0","tid":28373,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:54:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9aad77b338d35206a1cb9dfbb826fc1ae57fe497","tid":28373,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e50c004a15530481c59f69119fca69c8c3a3b71","tid":28373,"uid":642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:59:11.000Z","msg":"有fd試過 仆埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bdaf48e8f2b33efb889a6ab3a01fbcc1845e670","tid":28373,"uid":51076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T01:59:20.000Z","msg":"帽事既"},{"pid":"7a15bff67e531498b144e417fbc36155986c9844","tid":28373,"uid":38997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:00:01.000Z","msg":"帽事既"},{"pid":"f21a2f3fe735568946a44d24dea75ff1bd18b8c6","tid":28373,"uid":54018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-08T02:01:10.000Z","msg":"男女之間當然有純友誼<br />\n不過佢地後來做左情侶<br 